{"id":26016697,"date":"2026-01-30T17:39:03","date_gmt":"2026-01-30T12:09:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/?p=26016697"},"modified":"2026-02-26T13:06:52","modified_gmt":"2026-02-26T07:36:52","slug":"bcom-professional-subjects-list","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list","title":{"rendered":"BCom Professional Syllabus 2026: All Semester Subjects List India"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_82_2 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#What_is_a_BCom_Professional\" >What is a BCom Professional?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#BCom_Professional_1st_Year_Syllabus_Sem_1_2_Subjects\" >BCom Professional: 1st Year Syllabus (Sem 1 &amp; 2 Subjects)<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#1st_Year_Course_Overview_Structure\" >1st Year Course Overview &amp; Structure<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#BCom_Professional_1st_2nd_Semester_Subjects\" >BCom Professional: 1st &amp; 2nd Semester Subjects<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#BCom_Professional_2nd_Year_Syllabus_Sem_3_4_Subjects\" >BCom Professional: 2nd Year Syllabus (Sem 3 &amp; 4 Subjects)<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#2nd_Year_Course_Overview_Structure\" >2nd Year Course Overview &amp; Structure<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#BCom_Professional_3rd_4th_Semester_Subjects\" >BCom Professional: 3rd &amp; 4th Semester Subjects<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#BCom_Professional_3rd_Year_Syllabus_Sem_5_6_Subjects\" >BCom Professional: 3rd Year Syllabus (Sem 5 &amp; 6 Subjects)<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#3rd_Year_Course_Overview_Structure\" >3rd Year Course Overview &amp; Structure<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#BCom_Professional_5th_6th_Semester_Subjects\" >BCom Professional: 5th &amp; 6th Semester Subjects&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\/#FAQs\" >FAQs<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>A B.Com Professional course is a specialised Bachelor of Commerce degree program designed for students seeking a more direct and faster path to career opportunities in finance, accounting, and management.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The program integrates regular Commerce subjects with professional qualifications like CS, CA, or CIMA. Some of the key BCom Professional subjects covered in the course syllabus include Financial Accounting, Taxation, Strategic Business Reporting, Performance Management, Research Methodology, and International Business Management, among others.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This blog takes a close look at the complete BCom Professional syllabus across all six semesters of the three-year program. This would help you better understand the course content and make an informed decision on whether you are a suitable fit for the program.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_is_a_BCom_Professional\"><\/span><strong>What is a BCom Professional?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A BCom Professional degree is an integrated commerce program offered to students at the undergraduate level. The program is a perfect blend of a regular BCom degree and professional accounting certifications.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The idea is to help students save time (and money) on earning these certifications separately. Students pursuing the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/online-bcom-professional-mahe\"><strong>BCom Professional degree program online<\/strong><\/a> can thus gain entry into rewarding careers in the following fields faster:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Key Job Profiles After BCom Professional<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>Top Industries<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>Financial Analysis<\/td><td>BFSI<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Auditing&nbsp;<\/td><td>Accounting &amp; Auditing Firms&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Tax Consultancy&nbsp;<\/td><td>Consulting<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Management Accountancy&nbsp;<\/td><td>Manufacturing &amp; FMCG<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Forensic Accountancy<\/td><td>Healthcare &amp; Hospitals<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Corporate Finance&nbsp;<\/td><td>Telecommunications&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Compliance Management<\/td><td>Startups &amp; FinTech<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Banking Operations<\/td><td>Government &amp; Public Sector<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Financial Planning<\/td><td>E-Commerce &amp; Retail<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Risk Analysis<\/td><td>IT &amp; Services<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BCom_Professional_1st_Year_Syllabus_Sem_1_2_Subjects\"><\/span><strong>BCom Professional: 1st Year Syllabus (Sem 1 &amp; 2 Subjects)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A BCom Professional program typically spans 3 years at most institutions. The first-year BCom Professional subjects list comprises a mix of foundational concepts in core commerce and topics that align with global professional certifications, such as ACCA\/CIMA.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1st_Year_Course_Overview_Structure\"><\/span><strong>1st Year Course Overview &amp; Structure<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Key Subjects: <\/strong>Financial Accounting, Managerial Economics, Financial Reporting, Environmental Studies, and more.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Learning Objectives:<\/strong> To strengthen the foundation of students in core commerce subjects integrated with professional certifications.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Skills Learned by Students: <\/strong>Proficiency in data and tech, problem-solving, time management, critical thinking and analysis, innovation, and financial literacy, among others.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BCom_Professional_1st_2nd_Semester_Subjects\"><\/span><strong>BCom Professional: 1st &amp; 2nd Semester Subjects<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Shared below is the complete BCom Professional Accounting subjects list in the first and second semesters (Year 1) of the program:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th><strong>Semesters&nbsp;<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>Subjects<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><br><strong>1st Semester&nbsp;<\/strong><\/td><td>Business And Technology<br>Financial Accounting<br>Management Accounting<br>Business Communication<br>Managerial Economics<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><br><strong>2nd Semester<\/strong><\/td><td>Business Statistics and Mathematics<br>Financial Reporting<br>Taxation<br>Analytics Using Computer Applications<br>Environmental Studies<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BCom_Professional_2nd_Year_Syllabus_Sem_3_4_Subjects\"><\/span><strong>BCom Professional: 2nd Year Syllabus (Sem 3 &amp; 4 Subjects)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Year 2 of the BCom Professional subjects aims to allow students to dive deeper into the core commerce concepts already covered in the first two semesters of the program. Students are prepared to become job-ready in the future by learning advanced concepts in commerce and their professional applications.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2nd_Year_Course_Overview_Structure\"><\/span><strong>2nd Year Course Overview &amp; Structure<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>2nd Year Subjects:<\/strong> Financial Management, Strategic Business Reporting, Marketing Management, Performance Management, and Cybersecurity in Finance are some of the many subjects covered in the third and fourth semesters of the program.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Learning Objectives:<\/strong> To offer students advanced learning in taxation, accounting, and law, and also develop analytical skills in learners, which prepares them for corporate roles in relevant industries.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Skills Learned by Students: <\/strong>Financial analysis and management, digital proficiency, business communication, research methodology, adaptability, professionalism, entrepreneurship, etc.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BCom_Professional_3rd_4th_Semester_Subjects\"><\/span><strong>BCom Professional: 3rd &amp; 4th Semester Subjects<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out the complete BCom Professional subjects list for the second year in the table below:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Semesters<\/th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Subjects<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"><strong>3rd Semester<\/strong><\/td><td>Audit and Assurance<br><br>Financial Management<br><br>Corporate and Business Law<br><br>Strategic Business Reporting<br><br>Cybersecurity in Finance<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"><strong>4th Semester<br><\/strong><br><br><\/td><td>Performance Management<br><br>Strategic Business Leader<br><br>Marketing Management<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"><strong>Electives (choice of any one subject)<\/strong><\/td><td>Project Management<br><br>Indian Taxation<br><br>Operations Management<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BCom_Professional_3rd_Year_Syllabus_Sem_5_6_Subjects\"><\/span><strong>BCom Professional: 3rd Year Syllabus (Sem 5 &amp; 6 Subjects)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Students in the third and final year of the BCom Professional program start focusing on more advanced and specialized topics. These subjects generally integrate preparation for professional certifications with a combination of project-based learning.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3rd_Year_Course_Overview_Structure\"><\/span><strong>3rd Year Course Overview &amp; Structure<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Core Subjects: <\/strong>Sustainable Business Models and Circular Economy, Advanced Audit and Assurance, and Corporate Governance and Business Ethics are some of the topics covered in the 3rd year.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Electives\/<\/strong><strong>Specializations: <\/strong>Advanced Financial Management, Entrepreneurship and Startup Ecosystem, and Project II.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Learning Objectives: <\/strong>To impart specialized and advanced concepts in taxation, accounting, and financial management to students, which align with professional certifications.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Skills Learned by Students: <\/strong>Financial modeling, data analysis, financial reporting, advanced accounting, strategic decision-making, leadership, project management, and advanced communication skills.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Internships and Projects: <\/strong>Internships in the final year of the program are essential for students to build hands-on professional skills in varied related domains. They also help them secure pre-placement offers. Projects are generally focused on research and help students build research and analytical skills.<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BCom_Professional_5th_6th_Semester_Subjects\"><\/span><strong>BCom Professional: 5th &amp; 6th Semester Subjects<\/strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The 5th and 6th semesters of the final year offer advanced concepts, project studies, and a choice of electives, too, as shared in the table below:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><thead><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Semesters<\/th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Core Subjects<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"><strong>5th Semester<\/strong><\/td><td>Research Methodology<br>Sustainable Business Models and Circular Economy<br>Advanced Performance Management<br>Advanced Audit and Assurance<br>Project \u2013 I<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"><strong>6th Semester<\/strong><\/td><td>International Business Management<br>Corporate Governance and Business Ethics<br>Security Analysis &amp; Portfolio Management<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Electives (choice of any one subject)<\/strong><\/td><td>Advanced Financial Management<br>Entrepreneurship and Startup Ecosystem<br>Project \u2013 II<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Related Blog<\/strong>: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/what-is-bcom-professional-a-beginners-guide\">What is BCom (Professional)? A Beginner\u2019s Guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FAQs\"><\/span><strong>FAQs<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. Which subjects are taught in the first year of BCom Professional?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The first year of BCom Professional Accounting courses is divided into two semesters. Each semester offers 5 subjects, totaling 10 in the entire year. They are as follows:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1st Semester<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Business And Technology<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Financial Accounting<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Management Accounting<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Business Communication<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Managerial Economics<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2nd Semester<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Business Statistics and Mathematics<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Financial Reporting<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Taxation<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Analytics Using Computer Applications<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Environmental Studies<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. Is a BCom Professional a good option?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, pursuing a specialized degree program such as the BCom Professional is a perfect choice for undergraduate students. This is because the course is a perfect combination of foundational concepts in commerce aligned with professional certifications such as CA or CS, paving the way for advanced studies or careers in diverse fields.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Can I take a BCom Professional course online?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Absolutely! You can easily pursue an Online BCom Professional course from any part of the world on the Online Manipal platform. Manipal Academy of Higher Education (MAHE) offers this specialized three-year degree course on the platform to students worldwide.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. What are the eligibility criteria for a BCom Professional?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Students aspiring to apply for the program must meet the following admission criteria:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Completion of 10+2\/intermediate\/senior secondary education from a recognized school board.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A 10+3 diploma from a recognized national or state institute, or an equivalent qualification, as recognized by the Association of Indian Universities, is also accepted in any discipline.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>At least 50% marks in 10+2\/10+3 is required from course applicants.&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. What are the elective subjects covered in the BCom Professional course?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Electives are offered to students in the 4th and 6th semesters of the program. Herein, students can choose any one subject of their liking to pursue a specialization in from the following:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4th Semester<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Project Management<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Indian Taxation<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Operations Management<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>6th Semester<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Advanced Financial Management<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Entrepreneurship and Startup Ecosystem<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Project \u2013 II<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>6. Is a BCom Professional easier compared to other BCom specializations?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A BCom Professional degree is different from the other specializations of BCom programs, though not necessarily easier. With integrated professional certification courses such as CIMA offered as part of the program curriculum, BCom Professional makes students job-ready faster.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>7. What is the average starting salary after completing a BCom Professional course?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The average salary for a popular entry-level role, such as a Financial Analyst, after graduating with a BCom Professional degree is estimated to be in the range of INR 4 LPA &#8211; INR 9 LPA (approx). The salaries for different professionals are likely to depend on various factors.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><strong>Source<\/strong>: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.glassdoor.co.in\/Salaries\/financial-analyst-salary-SRCH_KO0,17.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Glassdoor<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>8. How many semesters are there in a BCom Professional?&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The three-year program comprises six semesters. Each year contains two semesters.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A B.Com Professional course is a specialised Bachelor of Commerce degree program designed for students seeking a more direct and faster path to career opportunities in finance, accounting, and management.&nbsp; The program integrates regular Commerce subjects with professional qualifications like CS, CA, or CIMA. Some of the key BCom Professional subjects covered in the course [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":126,"featured_media":26017628,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[612],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-26016697","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-bcom"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>BCom Professional Syllabus (2026): All Semester Subjects List<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Check the complete BCom Professional Syllabus (2026) here. All semester subjects are listed clearly for easy study planning. Start prepping!\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26016697\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"BCom Professional Syllabus (2026): All Semester Subjects List\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Check the complete BCom Professional Syllabus (2026) here. All semester subjects are listed clearly for easy study planning. Start prepping!\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/bcom-professional-subjects-list\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:publisher\" content=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/onlinemanipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2026-01-30T12:09:03+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2026-02-26T07:36:52+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/BCom-Professional-Course-Syllabus-2025\u201326-All-Semester-Subjects-List-scaled.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"2560\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"847\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:type\" content=\"image\/jpeg\" \/>\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"Krishnanjali KU\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:label1\" content=\"Written by\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data1\" content=\"Krishnanjali KU\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:label2\" content=\"Estimated reading time\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data2\" content=\"6 minutes\" \/>\n<script type=\"application\/ld+json\" class=\"yoast-schema-graph\">{\"@context\":\"https:\\\/\\\/schema.org\",\"@gra